  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the ability to use pharmacogenetic testing in a
      joint replacement practice to prescribe the most effective pain medicine for a specific
      patient.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Enrolling by invitation</overall_status>
